title: Jeremy Tilse
text:
Jeremy Tilse (born 2 June 1986 in <a href="Newcastle%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Newcastle</a>, <a href="Australia">Australia</a>) is a <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> footballer. He plays for the <a href="New%20South%20Wales%20Waratahs">Waratahs</a> in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His regular playing position is <a href="prop%20%28rugby%20union%29">prop</a>.
He made his senior debut during the <a href="2007%20Super%2014%20season">2007 Super 14 season</a> against the <a href="Cheetahs%20%28rugby%20union%29">Cheetahs</a>. His cousin is former <a href="Canberra%20Raiders">Canberra Raiders</a> and current <a href="Hull%20Kingston%20Rovers">Hull Kingston Rovers</a> player <a href="Dane%20Tilse">Dane Tilse</a>.
